texts.content: {"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,13],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"拍手吸引注意小朋友们坐稳啦"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,22],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"今天的故事发生在很久很久以前那时天空可热闹啦"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,21],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"有十颗金光闪闪的小太阳像十个调皮的火球娃娃"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,14],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"它们不排队呼啦啦全挤到天上玩"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,18],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"云朵老人气得胡子打结大地像烤焦的饼干"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,22],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"咔嚓嚓裂开了缝地上的人们热得受不了小草蔫了头"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,5],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"河水快烧干"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,15],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"这时一个叫后羿的神箭手站了出来"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,23],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"他可不是普通人哦他有一把老祖母用星光编织的神弓"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,5],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"弓弦摸上去"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,19],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"像雨后彩虹般柔软还有九支月亮婆婆送的、"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,8],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"冰凉凉的月牙银箭"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,14],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"后羿深吸一口气搭上第一支银箭"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,12],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"咻箭飞出去带着雪花的清凉"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,17],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"一个小太阳噗地变成金色羽毛飘飘落下"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,9],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"天空瞬间暗了一点点"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,17],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"飘来一阵薄荷的清香后羿不停手咻咻咻"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,10],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"神箭一支接一支飞上天"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,16],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"金羽毛像下雨一样飘落天空渐渐凉快"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,19],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"当射到第九箭时最后一个太阳吓得脸都白了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,8],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"躲进云被子里发抖"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,9],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"云层被箭划过的痕迹"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,21],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"流出甜甜的晚霞蜜糖后羿心软了收起最后一支箭"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,12],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"小朋友们这时候大家明白了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,22],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"勇气和善良就像后羿的神箭能把最火热的困难融化"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,22],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"看现在天上那个温和的太阳就是知错就改的小太阳"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,9],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"每天乖乖升起落下呢"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,15],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"飘落的金羽毛变成了田里的向日葵"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,8],"size":7,"font":{"id":"","path":""},"strokes":[{"alpha":1,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1,"color":[0,0,0]}},"width":0.07999999821186066}]}],"text":"永远追着太阳微笑"}
